WEBVTT

01:35.800 --> 01:37.720
ADAPTED FROM THE NOVEL OF THE SAME NAME
BY ZHU YI ON WWW.JJWXC.NET

01:40.120 --> 01:41.920
NANWU NO. 1 HIGH SCHOOL
100TH ANNIVERSARY CELEBRATION

01:42.000 --> 01:43.440
- There are so many people.
- One more.

01:46.920 --> 01:48.560
- One more.
- Come and take a selfie with me.

01:48.640 --> 01:50.240
- Now.
- Okay.

01:55.760 --> 01:57.640
- Look.
- That's nice.

02:08.680 --> 02:09.880
Qiao.

02:10.680 --> 02:12.320
Dian. You're finally here.

02:12.400 --> 02:13.280
Come on.

02:13.800 --> 02:14.960
Come on.

02:15.040 --> 02:17.360
When can we visit your new home?

02:19.560 --> 02:20.800
In love?

02:21.680 --> 02:24.120
Good friends for now.
During the probation period.

02:24.640 --> 02:26.120
Can best friends hold each other's hands?

02:28.520 --> 02:30.600
- Of course.
- Yes, we can.

02:30.680 --> 02:32.240
- Of course.
- Yes, we can.

02:32.320 --> 02:33.880
Wen Shuangjiang.

02:33.960 --> 02:35.360
We're too slow.

02:35.440 --> 02:37.000
We should have held hands
earlier, like them.

02:38.040 --> 02:39.640
Bro. Stop.

02:39.720 --> 02:40.920
Probation period.

02:41.000 --> 02:42.520
She's hard to please. Give me some time.

02:42.600 --> 02:44.120
I'll tell you when it's done.

02:45.360 --> 02:46.360
Let's go for a walk. Lead the way.

02:46.440 --> 02:47.680
Okay. Let's go.

02:50.640 --> 02:51.760
Let's go.

02:51.840 --> 02:52.800
Let's go.

02:52.880 --> 02:54.160
Boys and girls,

02:54.240 --> 02:57.080
your illustrious alumnus,
Su Haoan, is back.

02:57.160 --> 02:58.480
He's so confident.

02:59.400 --> 03:01.600
With Zhong Siqiao, your schoolmate,

03:01.680 --> 03:03.720
although she's a bit old.

03:03.800 --> 03:05.600
What did you say?

03:05.680 --> 03:07.080
Zhong Siqiao, run.

03:09.320 --> 03:11.080
- That's nice.
- Stop right there.

03:28.800 --> 03:31.400
If we met at the graduation ceremony,

03:32.920 --> 03:34.920
would we go around
taking pictures like them?

03:39.000 --> 03:41.120
Excuse me. Excuse me.

03:52.320 --> 03:54.000
Wen Shuangjiang.

04:20.839 --> 04:22.079
Excuse me.

04:23.520 --> 04:26.120
Do you know where Senior Class 17 is?

04:28.440 --> 04:29.560
I'm a freshman.

04:29.640 --> 04:30.680
I know.

04:31.200 --> 04:33.960
You're Sang Yan's beloved schoolmate.

04:35.960 --> 04:38.440
Go down and turn left
to enter the building.

04:38.520 --> 04:40.760
- How?
- Do you want me to take you there?

04:59.720 --> 05:01.120
Nothing's changed.

05:07.000 --> 05:09.760
Do you want to revisit the classroom?

05:29.200 --> 05:31.920
- Sang Yan?
- My name is Wen Yifan, sir.

05:32.560 --> 05:33.400
Sir.

05:35.040 --> 05:36.400
Sorry. I'm late.

05:36.480 --> 05:39.400
- It's him.
- Late for the first day of school?

05:40.480 --> 05:41.320
Did you two come together?

05:41.400 --> 05:43.160
No, we didn't.

05:43.240 --> 05:45.720
I just got lost,
so I searched for a while.

05:45.800 --> 05:47.480
What about you? Your reason?

05:50.560 --> 05:53.040
My dad didn't know I was a senior,
so he sent me to my middle school.

05:57.560 --> 05:59.600
Going in or not? Sang Yan.

06:00.760 --> 06:02.440
As a senior, I'll let you in first.

06:03.360 --> 06:04.560
Junior middle school boy.

06:09.920 --> 06:11.160
Wen Yifan is here.

06:12.160 --> 06:14.360
Sir. Sang Yan is here.

06:17.120 --> 06:20.760
STRIVE FOR SUCCESS
TIME WAITS FOR NO ONE

06:38.440 --> 06:40.040
Okay. We're all here.

06:40.120 --> 06:44.200
Please come up to the podium
and introduce yourselves to each other.

06:44.280 --> 06:45.960
We'll start with student No. 1.

06:46.680 --> 06:47.680
- Feng Jiaying.
- Yes.

06:47.760 --> 06:49.400
- Come on.
- Let's welcome her.

06:54.160 --> 06:55.520
Hello, everyone. My name is Feng Jiaying.

06:55.600 --> 06:57.800
My hobbies are singing and dancing.

06:57.880 --> 06:59.000
I'm a Taurus.

06:59.760 --> 07:02.320
I hope I can be good friends
with you all in the next three years.

07:02.400 --> 07:03.600
Thank you all.

07:05.120 --> 07:06.000
Very good.

07:07.000 --> 07:10.680
Next is Wen Yifan. Let's welcome her.

07:18.600 --> 07:19.960
Hello, everyone. My name is Wen Yifan.

07:20.840 --> 07:22.440
My hobby is dancing.

07:22.520 --> 07:24.280
My nickname is Shuangjiang.

07:24.960 --> 07:26.800
On the day I was born,

07:26.880 --> 07:28.960
it happened to be the First Frost,

07:29.040 --> 07:30.280
so my dad gave me this nickname.

07:30.360 --> 07:31.400
Thank you.

07:35.080 --> 07:37.120
Okay. Next, Sang Yan. Okay? Come on.

07:37.200 --> 07:38.400
Sang Yan.

07:38.480 --> 07:40.080
- Okay.
- Come on. Let's welcome him.

07:48.320 --> 07:50.480
Hello everyone. My name is Sang Yan.

07:50.560 --> 07:51.560
I can't dance,

07:53.720 --> 07:56.240
so I can only add two points. Okay.

07:58.920 --> 08:00.480
- The first point.
- OK.

08:00.560 --> 08:01.840
OK.

08:08.040 --> 08:10.320
These are the two points Sang Yan added.

08:10.400 --> 08:11.840
Okay? Remember these two points.

08:11.920 --> 08:15.800
The two points are for your friendship
in this class

08:15.880 --> 08:18.280
and your academic performance. Okay?

08:18.360 --> 08:19.880
- Okay.
- Okay.

08:27.800 --> 08:28.760
Are you tired?

08:29.280 --> 08:30.560
Going to hang out again?

08:33.440 --> 08:34.760
I want to stay here for a while.

08:50.880 --> 08:52.200
Why haven't you changed at all?

08:55.680 --> 08:58.280
If you haven't changed,
why are you asking me to?

09:16.240 --> 09:18.200
Why don't you leave?

09:18.280 --> 09:20.040
Hello.

09:20.120 --> 09:21.680
Hello.

09:21.760 --> 09:24.880
This time slot
is booked by the dance class.

09:24.960 --> 09:26.080
Is she a freshman?

09:26.160 --> 09:27.600
Whatever.

09:27.680 --> 09:29.560
She's not a good dancer,

09:29.640 --> 09:30.880
but she's cocky.

09:32.640 --> 09:34.360
This dance class is booked by us.

09:34.440 --> 09:35.600
You can leave now.

09:36.760 --> 09:38.680
Looks like there's ten minutes left.

09:39.280 --> 09:40.320
She refuses to leave.

09:40.840 --> 09:41.880
Overweening.

09:41.960 --> 09:44.760
You're dancing alone
while taking up all this space.

09:44.840 --> 09:47.040
- That's not necessary.
- Of course not.

09:47.120 --> 09:48.920
She's always like that.

09:50.200 --> 09:51.600
Didn't she say she had ten minutes left?

09:54.280 --> 09:58.120
And who said she was alone?

09:59.520 --> 10:00.640
Is she your girlfriend?

10:01.440 --> 10:02.440
No.

10:02.960 --> 10:05.720
Then why did you stand up for her
and fight for those ten minutes?

10:06.400 --> 10:08.560
Besides, you're not in the dance class.

10:09.480 --> 10:10.480
But I could be.

10:10.560 --> 10:12.640
I practiced martial arts when I was a kid,

10:12.720 --> 10:13.640
but they didn't want me.

10:17.240 --> 10:18.360
Are you in love with him?

10:20.240 --> 10:23.040
You two shouldn't be so close at school,

10:23.960 --> 10:25.080
lest people get you guys wrong.

10:27.200 --> 10:28.880
Don't let me see you like this again.

10:31.920 --> 10:33.160
Otherwise, I'll be rude.

10:34.360 --> 10:35.440
I'm sorry, sir.

10:58.200 --> 10:59.360
What do you want?

11:00.360 --> 11:01.400
To go back to class.

11:03.280 --> 11:05.160
Can you keep your distance from me then?

11:06.280 --> 11:07.960
OK. How far?

11:15.880 --> 11:18.000
Why do you keep secretly following me?

11:19.120 --> 11:21.040
I'm following you openly.

11:25.760 --> 11:26.720
Your shoelace is untied.

11:27.800 --> 11:29.520
Your shoelace is untied.

11:43.080 --> 11:45.000
Yan, the ice is here.

11:47.560 --> 11:50.400
- So, where are we going to sit?
- On the chair.

12:17.480 --> 12:20.400
Don't you need to study

12:21.280 --> 12:22.600
or play basketball

12:23.680 --> 12:25.000
besides following me?

12:25.920 --> 12:28.880
I'm going to take the bus.

12:28.960 --> 12:30.160
The same direction when I go home.

13:26.280 --> 13:27.520
Mr. Zhang wants to see you.

13:34.480 --> 13:35.640
Wen Shuangjiang.

13:36.720 --> 13:37.560
Shoes.

13:40.160 --> 13:41.160
Thank you.

13:44.280 --> 13:45.280
School's out?

13:46.040 --> 13:47.240
Sang Yan, can you

13:47.320 --> 13:50.640
turn your passion
into motivation for your endeavors?

13:50.720 --> 13:52.560
It's not too late for you to fall in love

13:52.640 --> 13:53.760
when you go to college and mature a bit.

13:54.520 --> 13:55.360
Listen.

13:55.440 --> 13:56.600
After you transfer,

13:56.680 --> 13:58.920
you have to completely
cut ties with this kid.

13:59.000 --> 13:59.840
Do you hear me?

14:30.720 --> 14:31.760
Why are we here?

14:32.800 --> 14:33.800
You don't have a place to dance,

14:33.880 --> 14:36.280
so just make do here.

14:56.320 --> 14:57.720
I'm painting wings.

14:58.960 --> 15:01.920
Later, the scars will fly away.

15:16.240 --> 15:17.720
Whether you'll show up or not,

15:18.760 --> 15:20.400
I'm still doing what I promised.

15:57.480 --> 15:59.400
Wake up. It's too late.

16:03.040 --> 16:04.000
Class is over?

16:05.560 --> 16:06.640
I have to erase the blackboard.

16:10.920 --> 16:12.240
When did you change
into your school uniform?

16:21.120 --> 16:23.640
WHEN YOU'RE OLD

16:28.480 --> 16:30.360
GRAY AND SLEEPY

16:30.440 --> 16:32.480
YOU SNUGGLE WEARILY BY THE FIRESIDE
AND TAKE A RANDOM BOOK FOR COMPANY

16:32.560 --> 16:35.840
ELEGANT PAST… A MAN ONCE GAZED…

16:47.240 --> 16:48.200
Morning.

16:51.960 --> 16:52.800
Sit over there.

16:52.880 --> 16:55.360
- Why? You were not in my class.
- Now.

17:08.839 --> 17:10.960
Now, looking back on it, I don't know
if I'm remembering correctly.

17:11.040 --> 17:12.359
That year,

17:12.440 --> 17:14.520
I asked a very strange question.

17:14.599 --> 17:16.079
Thinking about that now, as a teacher,

17:16.160 --> 17:17.160
I realize I shouldn't
have been so gossipy.

17:17.240 --> 17:18.079
Gossipy for what?

17:18.160 --> 17:20.359
When the two were late together that time

17:20.440 --> 17:22.560
and stood at the door, I asked them,

17:22.640 --> 17:24.240
"Did you come together?"

17:25.800 --> 17:28.880
Then, I remember Wen Yifan
immediately denying it, "No."

17:28.960 --> 17:31.080
Actually, I think I might have been

17:31.160 --> 17:33.640
a little bit nosy or a little bit abrupt

17:33.720 --> 17:34.920
when I asked that question,

17:35.000 --> 17:36.400
but it didn't occur to me

17:36.480 --> 17:38.200
that the two would actually go this far,

17:38.280 --> 17:40.680
so I was the prophet.

17:41.480 --> 17:45.040
The first time I met her
was at school. I was like,

17:45.120 --> 17:48.320
"Wow, this girl is so beautiful.

17:48.400 --> 17:51.440
It would be just wonderful

17:51.520 --> 17:55.120
if she could be my daughter-in-law."

17:55.200 --> 17:57.200
When did you realize
the two were not right?

17:57.280 --> 18:02.600
Actually, I thought something was wrong

18:02.680 --> 18:04.520
when the bracelet was lost

18:04.600 --> 18:06.040
and he slipped it into that box.

18:06.560 --> 18:08.120
How did you know it was him?

18:08.200 --> 18:09.280
SMALL GESTURES YU ZHUOSUO SAW

18:09.360 --> 18:10.200
I got a sneak peek.

18:12.080 --> 18:14.360
What was your first visit to Overtime for?

18:14.440 --> 18:18.000
I first came to Overtime
to visit the owner with Dian.

18:18.080 --> 18:21.120
Can he be called
the signature of Overtime?

18:21.840 --> 18:23.600
BFF'S BLABBING

18:23.680 --> 18:24.880
Not in my opinion.

18:24.960 --> 18:26.440
Then who is?

18:27.520 --> 18:28.600
Who…

18:29.640 --> 18:30.800
Qian Fei?

18:31.480 --> 18:32.520
Maybe Yu Zhuo.

18:33.200 --> 18:35.040
When did you realize those two were weird?

18:35.120 --> 18:38.200
Maybe at a dinner.

18:38.280 --> 18:40.160
Sang Yan texted,

18:40.240 --> 18:42.440
but Wen Yifan came over.

18:42.520 --> 18:44.040
I didn't think much of it at the time,

18:44.120 --> 18:46.040
but I didn't expect them
to publicize their relationship

18:46.120 --> 18:47.240
at my wedding.

18:47.320 --> 18:49.040
I felt like

18:49.560 --> 18:50.960
the sauce was better

18:51.480 --> 18:54.320
than the fish at my wedding.

18:54.400 --> 18:57.160
I was angry,
but still wanted to wish them well

18:57.240 --> 18:58.320
and hope they could
get along better and better.

18:58.400 --> 19:00.480
We've all been following the story

19:00.560 --> 19:02.120
between Sang Yan and Wen Yifan

19:02.200 --> 19:05.200
because fate is actually
a very wonderful thing.

19:05.280 --> 19:08.880
And I think two people,
especially two people who are in love,

19:08.960 --> 19:12.000
will really encounter some setbacks

19:12.080 --> 19:15.240
or trials or even big hurdles,

19:15.320 --> 19:17.360
but the more such trials,

19:17.440 --> 19:20.200
the more they can map out

19:20.280 --> 19:21.640
the sweetness of their future.

19:21.720 --> 19:23.000
The time Wen Yifan disappeared…

19:23.080 --> 19:24.000
SU HAOAN TALKS A LOT

19:24.080 --> 19:25.560
…and went to Hong Kong, China,

19:25.640 --> 19:28.160
I could feel he was
particularly flustered.

19:28.760 --> 19:30.480
He has always been so calm

19:30.560 --> 19:32.160
and not easily seen with his emotions,

19:32.960 --> 19:38.640
but during that period, all his emotions
seemed to be obvious.

19:38.720 --> 19:41.080
A lot of times, I just

19:41.160 --> 19:43.000
superficially told him that he'd be okay

19:43.080 --> 19:44.560
and hoped that he'd be okay,

19:45.080 --> 19:47.000
but I knew that he was really upset.

19:47.080 --> 19:51.320
Eventually, however,
they found each other.

19:51.920 --> 19:53.200
During the New Year's Eve dinner,

19:53.280 --> 19:55.880
I had a secret conversation with Yifan

19:55.960 --> 19:58.280
about my brother's high school days.

19:58.360 --> 20:00.760
At that time, I was very depressed

20:00.840 --> 20:02.920
because I saw that he,

20:03.000 --> 20:05.760
who was usually very proud and cheerful,

20:05.840 --> 20:08.320
was hit at that time,

20:08.400 --> 20:10.880
fell into the lowest point of his life,

20:10.960 --> 20:13.000
and became very upset every day.

20:13.080 --> 20:17.320
I felt, as his sister, very sad about it.

20:17.400 --> 20:19.480
The look in his eyes
when he fell in love with someone

20:19.560 --> 20:20.680
was especially different.

20:21.640 --> 20:23.960
When he saw Wen Yifan, his concealment

20:24.960 --> 20:27.360
of his true emotions

20:27.440 --> 20:29.760
became apparent.

20:30.360 --> 20:32.640
Wen Yifan looks gentle
but is actually tough,

20:32.720 --> 20:36.360
whilst Sang Yan is just the opposite,

20:36.440 --> 20:38.960
so the two complement
each other quite well

20:39.040 --> 20:40.120
and are a perfect match.

20:41.320 --> 20:43.440
The two are getting married,

20:43.520 --> 20:46.200
so, do you want
to give them your blessing?

20:46.280 --> 20:48.520
‪ALWAYS WITH YOU

20:48.600 --> 20:49.600
I hope

20:50.600 --> 20:52.120
Sang Yan

20:52.720 --> 20:54.200
can stay with Dian

20:54.840 --> 20:56.240
forever

20:58.720 --> 21:02.400
and never let her be sad
or depressed again.

21:02.480 --> 21:05.640
I hope she can be

21:07.200 --> 21:08.880
truly happy forever.

21:08.960 --> 21:10.760
I thought of a poem.

21:11.960 --> 21:13.800
When rain falls on this city

21:13.880 --> 21:15.240
The two share one umbrella

21:15.320 --> 21:17.240
HAPPY FOREVER

21:17.320 --> 21:19.600
I wish Yan to be happy forever.

21:20.680 --> 21:22.200
I certainly wish

21:22.280 --> 21:25.400
they could grow old together
and have children soon.

21:25.920 --> 21:28.480
More than one. Have many.

21:28.560 --> 21:30.160
I hope their children

21:30.920 --> 21:32.680
can inherit their fine…

21:32.760 --> 21:35.040
fine tradi… fine genes,

21:35.120 --> 21:36.920
meaning they will be good-looking.

21:37.000 --> 21:38.280
If you two are going to get married,

21:38.360 --> 21:40.600
I must wish you
a hundred years of good luck.

21:40.680 --> 21:44.400
And be sure to love each other
happily for a long time.

21:44.480 --> 21:47.200
Sang Yan'd better comfort Wen Yifan often,

21:47.280 --> 21:49.960
or I might steal Wen Yifan away. Remember.

21:54.560 --> 21:58.560
If Wen Yifan is the only princess
left in this world,

21:58.640 --> 22:03.200
Sang Yan will be the last knight
in this world.

22:04.240 --> 22:06.800
I wish that they will never fight

22:06.880 --> 22:10.160
and that whatever comes their way,
they will resolve it very well.

22:10.240 --> 22:12.080
Happy every day. Happy forever.

22:12.160 --> 22:15.880
What will you do if Sang Yan
treats Wen Yifan badly?

22:15.960 --> 22:17.760
I definitely
wouldn't let him off the hook.

22:18.680 --> 22:19.560
I would

22:20.360 --> 22:21.200
beat him up.

22:22.520 --> 22:24.840
I hope Sang Yan treats Wen Yifan well.

22:26.040 --> 22:27.040
Wen Yifan

22:27.120 --> 22:30.240
will definitely be
the best girl in his life.

22:31.160 --> 22:33.120
How many kids do you
want them to have in the future?

22:33.920 --> 22:36.680
As many as they want.
I'm very open-minded.

22:36.760 --> 22:39.600
They can have as many as they want.

22:39.680 --> 22:41.640
They're getting married now,

22:41.720 --> 22:44.560
finally, so what are you thinking now?

22:46.160 --> 22:48.080
How much money
should I put in the red envelope?

22:48.960 --> 22:52.840
WEN SHUANGJIANG, NOW IT'S MY TURN

23:02.640 --> 23:03.880
How long have you been preparing?

23:06.680 --> 23:07.640
However long that is,

23:10.120 --> 23:11.240
you're worth it.

23:28.120 --> 23:29.080
It's for you.

23:41.720 --> 23:44.480
This is… Dancing-Doll Orchid.

23:45.920 --> 23:46.920
Because to me,

23:50.520 --> 23:52.280
you look like a fluttering butterfly.

23:58.080 --> 23:59.720
You always shine.

24:01.920 --> 24:03.000
I want you

24:04.200 --> 24:05.760
to fly free forever.

24:08.840 --> 24:11.960
I want, like I said,

24:16.600 --> 24:18.040
to give you wings

24:21.080 --> 24:22.080
and destroy all your pain.

24:32.480 --> 24:33.720
I will always catch you.

24:38.120 --> 24:39.040
Okay.

24:44.400 --> 24:45.400
Wen Shuangjiang.

24:52.240 --> 24:53.080
I'll make you a promise.

25:40.880 --> 25:43.320
Here. You gave this to me,
but even you forgot it.

25:44.280 --> 25:45.640
Put it here so it can turn.

25:53.880 --> 25:55.320
- Okay.
- So deceptive.

25:59.440 --> 26:00.680
Dude, take it easy.

26:02.760 --> 26:03.680
It's out of battery.

26:09.080 --> 26:10.000
Forget it.

26:12.040 --> 26:13.080
Come on.

26:22.320 --> 26:23.320
Wen Shuangjiang.

26:29.680 --> 26:31.080
I'll make you a promise.

26:36.880 --> 26:38.080
After you marry me,

26:41.280 --> 26:42.720
all your wishes will come true.

26:44.520 --> 26:45.480
So you…

26:54.760 --> 26:55.760
You know

26:55.840 --> 26:58.160
what I want to say, right?

27:09.880 --> 27:10.840
Marry me.

27:41.440 --> 27:42.480
You're the only one I want to marry.

28:44.600 --> 28:46.200
Later, I realized

28:46.280 --> 28:48.400
Sang Yan picked this ring

28:48.480 --> 28:49.960
in the shape of a ribbon.

28:51.600 --> 28:53.040
He said

28:54.520 --> 28:58.320
it's because
we're each other's most precious gift.

29:01.440 --> 29:02.600
When you're old,

29:03.280 --> 29:04.560
gray,

29:05.360 --> 29:06.720
- Enough.
- and sleepy,

29:06.800 --> 29:08.800
you snuggle wearily by the fireside

29:10.000 --> 29:11.360
and take a random book for company.

29:12.520 --> 29:13.760
You savored the look in your eyes

29:13.840 --> 29:16.280
when you were chasing your dreams.

29:17.200 --> 29:19.200
You used to have that look

29:19.720 --> 29:21.280
and were full of affection.

29:23.880 --> 29:26.720
I loved your great and elegant past,

29:27.800 --> 29:29.480
your mistakes,

29:30.000 --> 29:31.560
and your true beauty.

29:33.120 --> 29:35.400
There is only one man who has ever gazed

29:35.480 --> 29:37.160
into your pious and holy heart

29:37.800 --> 29:39.640
and fallen in love

29:40.520 --> 29:43.280
with your sad and aging face.

29:46.160 --> 29:48.080
In the moonlight,
you bowed your head, stooped,

29:49.440 --> 29:51.240
and murmured dejectedly in an attempt

29:51.920 --> 29:53.120
to escape from love.

29:55.040 --> 29:57.080
Then you sneaked over the hill

29:57.720 --> 29:59.160
and hid your face…

29:59.240 --> 30:00.600
"…someone who is fierce and will love me…"

30:00.680 --> 30:02.280
…among the stars.

30:02.920 --> 30:04.320
"…until death…

30:04.400 --> 30:05.320
ORANGES ARE NOT THE ONLY FRUIT

30:06.160 --> 30:08.400
…and know that love is as strong as death

30:09.320 --> 30:12.560
and be on my side for ever and ever."

30:15.040 --> 30:16.120
I'm sorry.

30:17.520 --> 30:18.480
Are you okay?

30:25.800 --> 30:27.760
What are you reading? You're so focused.

30:30.080 --> 30:31.200
Are you that curious?

30:41.360 --> 30:44.760
ORANGES ARE NOT THE ONLY FRUIT

31:01.600 --> 31:05.960
I want someone who is fierce
and will love me until death.

31:07.080 --> 31:08.120
It's you.

31:13.480 --> 31:16.920
THE END

34:00.640 --> 34:01.480
HUGE THANKS TO EVERYONE INVOLVED
AND TO ALL THE FANS OF THE FIRST FROST!

34:01.560 --> 34:02.400
TREAT YOURSELF WELL
AND THE WORLD WILL HOLD MORE LOVE FOR YOU!
